Where's that mouse picture when you need it...cause that's what's happening to all of us. (unless of course you're wise enough to invest in petro stocks for your "refund")
I typed it with you in mind Bud !

anyone wanna rent a tanker and take a trip

You fellas rent it i'll drive it !?! No matter how you look at it we are getting HOSED!  I spent 190 dollars on gas to get to and from work this week, maybe i should quit and go work at mc d's across the street i'll take home more money.

I know gas is quite expensive but what are the reasons behind europe being double then most places? Are they making more money then us , or are other things cheaper there that we pay more for here?Does it just cost more to get the gas there? Or do they use more gas then us here in canada?
Those country's are the size of a postage stamp. Drive 50 miles and your across their country. 10 billion profit  , Where getting ripped off   no matter how you look at it!!!  .

The Euro is trading at about 1.50Dollars/Euro.  Most things are more expensive, alot of the added expense is due to higher taxes.  Also as a side point there wages are comparible to ours, however most people do the 99 year mortgage thing and pas their place and mortgage onto the kids.
